ch.epfl.lasec.mova
Class MovaPublicKey

java.lang.Object
  ch.epfl.lasec.mova.MovaPublicKey

public class MovaPublicKey
extends java.lang.Object

Class representing the public key in MOVA. The public key consits of

(Xgroup,Ygroup, d, seedK, (Ykey_1,...,Ykey_Lkey))
In this implementation, Xgroup is (Z/nZ)*, Ygroup is {-1,+1) and so d = 2.

Author:
Sebastien Duc

getEncoded

public byte[] getEncoded()
Get the encoded form of the public key.
The key is encoded in the following way (note: [x] is the encoded form of x)
.................................................................................................
|[seedK].length | [seedK] | [[n].length].length | [[n].length] | [n] | [Ykey_1] ... [Ykey_Lkey] |
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''

Returns:
Returns the encoded form of the public key.
